body_html: Assigning to Pete, since I believe he set up the inception5h.zip which has the raw GraphDef rather than the MetaGraph. I don't know how to regenerate the MetaGraph for inception easily. Presumably someone could take an inception model from github.com/tensorflow/models.git and do this for us as a learning exercise, if Pete or someone else doesn't get to it.
